OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777838750
OL,3,CPrayers and messages of support
OL,4,Creceived after Cathedral fire
OL,6,FLiverpool Anglican Cathedral has
OL,7,Fspoken out against online theories
OL,8,Fsuggesting a fire in its tower was a
OL,9,Fdeliberate attack.
OL,11,FVisitors were evacuated on Friday 1
OL,12,FMay, with firefighters tackling the
OL,13,Fblaze on a top-floor balcony.
OL,15,FMerseyside Fire and Rescue confirmed
OL,16,Fit was an electrical fire. There were
OL,17,Fno injuries and only minor damage.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/5
