CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777838750
OL,3,CPrayers and messages of support
OL,4,Creceived after Cathedral fire
OL,6,FPosts sharing the news on social media
OL,7,Fwere inundated with comments
OL,8,Fspeculating about the fire, receiving
OL,9,Fthousands of views and likes.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for the Cathedral said:
OL,12,F"Following the incident at Liverpool
OL,13,FCathedral, we are aware of speculation
OL,14,Fcirculating online.
OL,16,F"We want to reassure our community
OL,17,Fthat, based on the assessment of
OL,18,Femergency services, there is no
OL,19,Findication of any deliberate act.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777838750
OL,3,CPrayers and messages of support
OL,4,Creceived after Cathedral fire
OL,6,F"The incident was dealt with quickly
OL,7,Fand safely, with no injuries and only
OL,8,Fminimal damage.
OL,10,F"We are very grateful for the swift
OL,11,Fand professional response of
OL,12,FMerseyside Fire and Rescue Service."
OL,14,FEmergency services were called at
OL,15,F14.44 on Friday 1 May to to reports of
OL,16,Fa fire at the top of the tower, with
OL,17,Fsmoke visible.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
