CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777838750
OL,3,CPrayers and messages of support
OL,4,Creceived after Cathedral fire
OL,6,FCrews from Merseyside Fire and Rescue
OL,7,Farrived at the scene five minutes
OL,8,Flater and confirmed this was an
OL,9,Felectrical fire on the balcony on the
OL,10,Ftop floor of the cathedral.
OL,12,FFirefighters fought the fire, and the
OL,13,Fbuilding was evacuated.
OL,15,FBy 15.22 the fire was extinguished
OL,16,Fwith emergency workers leaving the
OL,17,Fscene just after 5pm.
OL,19,FThe Cathedral remains open and
OL,20,Fcontinues to welcome all who come
OL,21,Fthrough its doors.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
