PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1777838750
OL,3,CPrayers and messages of support
OL,4,Creceived after Cathedral fire
OL,6,FThe Tower is currently closed while
OL,7,Ffurther assessments are carried out.
OL,9,FA spokesperson from the Cathedral
OL,10,Ffurther adds: ""We are thankful for
OL,11,Fthe prayers and messages of support we
OL,12,Fhave received."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/5
